/t42/s16154/i","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16154%2Fi%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"such sums as are necessary for each of fiscal years 2011 through 2020.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"j","heading":"Targets","label":"j Targets","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16154/j","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16154","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16154%2Fj","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Not later than 180 days after , the Secretary shall establish targets for the program to address near-term (up to 2 years), mid-term (up to 7 years), and long-term (up to 15 years) challenges to the advancement of clean hydrogen systems and technologies.November 15, 2021","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
